Professional Prompt Library

Project Overview

The Professional Prompt Library is a curated collection of high-quality, reusable AI prompts designed for common professional tasks. The project demonstrates practical applications of Prompt Engineering using established frameworks such as ROLE, CREATE, and Chain of Thought (CoT).

This library serves as a professional toolkit that can be reused across business, legal, project management, marketing, and technical environments.



